Pinky Moabi, a Shell Ultra City franchisee, shares her inspiring story of entrepreneurship and personal growth. At a time when gaining any foothold in the local market is tough, Moabi explains how franchising can create a career path and open up key opportunities for determined individuals. “You are dealing with products that are tried and tested, and you get support and training from the franchisor,” she says. Brought to you by Nedbank Franchising.